{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/extras/punji.png?t=1738442881\" /><br><br><strong><u>Inspired by tactical shooters of the early 2000's, PunjiVR aims to mix their challenge and charm with new technologies and ideas to create a unique and unforgettable experience</u></strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/extras/nam.png?t=1738442881\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight for or against the <strong>US Army</strong>, <strong>NVA</strong>, and <strong>Vietcong</strong> (More factions coming soon!)<br><br></li><li> Battle in the <strong>streets, tunnels, rice paddies, jungle, and more!</strong> PunjiVR currently features over <u>15 unique missions</u> with many more on the way<br><br></li><li> Create your <strong>loadouts</strong> to best suit the mission. PunjiVR currently includes over <u>25 weapon and equipment items</u></li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/extras/heli.png?t=1738442881\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> PunjiVR currently features <u>4 flyable helicopters</u>:<br><strong>     - UH-1 &quot;Huey&quot; Transport<br>     - UH-1C Gunship<br>     - OH-6 &quot;Loach&quot;<br>     - AH-1 Cobra </strong><br><br></li><li> PunjiVR's flight model and controls are designed to be <strong>realistic but accessible </strong><br><br></li><li> Each helicopter's feel changes based on its model and the load (weapons, passengers, crew...) it's carrying</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/extras/other.png?t=1738442881\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <u><strong>Realistic Bullet Ballistics:</strong></u> <strong>Bullets penetrate</strong> based on material, caliber, and speed. They can also <strong>ricochet</strong> and <strong>lose velocity over time!</strong><br><br></li><li> <u><strong>Replayable Missions:</strong></u> Each level is designed to have more than one path to the objective. Enemy spawns are randomized and multiple playstyles are available to be tried and mastered.<br><br></li><li> <u><strong>No Hand Holding:</strong></u> Enemies will not always be easy to spot and they won't wait for you to shoot first. Take it slow, use cover, and most importantly, <i><u>keep your eyes peeled!</u></i><br><br></li><li> <u><strong>Long-Term Active Development:</strong></u> PunjiVR is a very ambitions project, especially for only one developer. I've spent the last two years creating, adding to, fixing, and polishing PunjiVR and I intend to continue doing so for many more years to come!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738442881","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738442881","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738442881","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738442881","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"PunjiVR depicts warfare and fighting, which includes minor violence in a stylized art format."},"detailed_description":"<h1>IMPORTANT!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>PunjiVR is being completely remade from the ground up as 'Version 2', which will be released as a free update. Owners of the game can test it out right now for free!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900020/extras/